2025-12-21 13:49:20.5824	2026-01-24 05:27:19.5683	27	5	289	222	\N	Riverside Psychedelic Summer Jam 2026	A Community Night of Music, Art & Vibes	### Event Overview\nCome together with your neighbors, friends, and fellow music lovers for an evening of live performances, creative energy, and good vibes all around. Expect groovy tunes, colorful performances, and lots of laughter! This is a space for everyone—families, friends, and curious minds alike.\n\n#### Location & Time\nThe festival takes place at **Riverside Park**, from **6:00 PM to 11:00 PM**. Bring a blanket, bring a friend, and let’s make some memories under the open sky.\n\n### Featured Band: Cosmic Treetop Collective\nThe **Cosmic Treetop Collective** blends swirling psych-rock with spacey melodies that will lift you off the ground. Get ready to sway, dance, and hum along with the stars.  \n\n#### Band Members:\n- Luna Rivera – Vocals & Synth  \n- Orion Beck – Guitar  \n- Sol Amari – Bass  \n- Nova Kim – Drums & Percussion  \n\n---\n\n### Evening Lineup\nHere’s the psychedelic ride we’ve lined up for the night:\n\n| Band / Artist               | Start Time |\n|-----------------------------|------------|\n| Cosmic Treetop Collective   | 18:30      |\n| The Velvet Ferns             | 19:30      |\n| Sunflower Nomads            | 20:30      |\n| DJ Electric Moonbeam         | 21:30      |\n\n---\n\n### Tickets & Entry\nTickets are available **online** or at the **door**.  \n**Doors open at 18:00**, so come early to grab a good spot and soak in the community vibes.  \n\n### Community Corner\n- Food trucks with vegetarian & vegan options  \n- Chill-out zones with blankets and hammocks  \n- Family-friendly spaces & creative workshops  \n- Bike parking and easy public transport access  \n\nLet’s come together for music, art, and connection—see you under the stars!	aaa	293	[SoundCodes~	soundcodes@grain.one	0176 59 97 80 74	https://soundcodes.grain.one	Home Studio	Friesische Straße	41	24937	Flensburg	DEU	SH	01010000